highlighting the main points and key information.\\n5. **Offer suggestions**: I can provide suggestions for things like gift ideas, travel destinations, books to read, or movies to watch.\\n6. **Chat and converse**: I can engage in natural-sounding conversations, using context and understanding to respond to questions and statements.\\n7. **Play games**: I can play simple text-based games with you, such as Hangman, 20 Questions, or Word Chain.\\n8. **Provide definitions**: I can define words and phrases, explaining their meanings and usage.\\n9. **Generate creative content**: I can create creative writing, such as poetry or short stories, or even compose music or dialogue.\\n10. **Help with language learning**: I can assist language learners by providing grammar corrections, vocabulary practice, and conversation exercises.\\n\\nWhat would you like me to help you with, Fernan?\\nHuman: whats my name again?",{"lc":1,"type":"155","id":"156"},"llama-3.3-70b-versatile","constructor",["157","158","159"],{"content":"160","additional_kwargs":"161","response_metadata":"162"},["157","158","163"],{"content":"164","tool_calls":"165","invalid_tool_calls":"166","additional_kwargs":"167","response_metadata":"168"},["157","158","159"],{"content":"169","additional_kwargs":"170","response_metadata":"171"},["157","158","163"],{"content":"106","tool_calls":"172","invalid_tool_calls":"173","additional_kwargs":"174","response_metadata":"175"},["157","158","159"],{"content":"176","additional_kwargs":"177","response_metadata":"178"},["157","158","163"],{"content":"179","tool_calls":"180","invalid_tool_calls":"181","additional_kwargs":"182","response_metadata":"183"},["157","158","159"],{"content":"160","additional_kwargs":"161","response_metadata":"162"},["157","158","163"],{"content":"164","tool_calls":"165","invalid_tool_calls":"166","additional_kwargs":"167","response_metadata":"168"},["157","158","159"],{"content":"169","additional_kwargs":"170","response_metadata":"171"},["157","158",